            "title": "美股日誌｜ 最後日記　道指微升　半導體受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜ 最後日記 道指微升 半導體受壓\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nQcSBrKQoJ0pHwi7MMrx0w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/8444d870-2c56-11f1-a7ff-c44d6ce0f60c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜ 最後日記 道指微升 半導體受壓</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國股市周一依然受壓，美國原油期貨自2022年以來首次收高於每桶100美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道指表現最叻，收市微升0.1%；標普500指數由升轉跌，下跌0.4%；以科技股為主的納斯達克綜合指數下跌0.7%。此前三大指數於上周收市表現疲弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">半導體板塊表現最差，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"美光科技\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:美光科技;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/MU/\">美光科技</a>（MU.US)大跌接近10%， <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"2\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"SanDisk\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:SanDisk;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/SNDK/\">SanDisk</a>（SNDK.US)則跌7%，市場擔憂內存市場價格出現明顯回落，令整個板塊延續上周跌勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"3\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"下載Yahoo財經APP\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=eDFkEhESdIhPGYRE2850\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-13818014-c911-484e-9cf8-21a75b971baf-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇<br/><br/></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月30日（星期一）市况</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"4\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"道瓊斯指數\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:道瓊斯指數;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI\"> 道瓊斯指數</a> 升49.5點或0.11%，報45,216.14點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"5\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"標普500指數\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC\"> 標普500指數</a> 跌25.13點或0.39%，報6,343.72點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"6\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"納斯達克指數\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克指數;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC\"> 納斯達克指數</a> 跌153.72點或0.73%，報20,794.64點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"7\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"紐約5月期油\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:紐約5月期油;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"> 紐約5月期油</a> 收報105.01美元一桶，升5.37美元或5.39%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"8\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"紐約4月期金\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"> 紐約4月期金</a> 收報4,540.4美元一盎司，升16.1美元或0.36%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"9\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"比特幣\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"> 比特幣</a> 截至美東時間下午4時報66,480.58美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"10\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"美國10年期國債息率\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"> 美國10年期國債息率</a> 收報4.342厘。<br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價周一上升，此前特朗普向《金融時報》表示，他傾向讓美國「無限期」控制伊朗石油產業。布蘭特原油期貨收於每桶 112 美元以上。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價急升，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"11\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"捷藍航空\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:捷藍航空;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/JBLU/\">捷藍航空</a>(JBLU.US)公布，由於伊朗戰爭導致航空燃油價格飆升，公司計劃提高行李托運費。 行業數據顯示，上周五芝加哥、休士頓、洛杉磯和紐約的燃料價格平均為每加侖4.57美元，比戰爭爆發前上漲約80%。捷藍航空收報跌2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周市場焦點集中於多項勞動市場指標，3 月就業報告即將公布。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這是最後一篇美股日誌，祝願Yahoo讀者繼續投資得心應手，贏到開巷。</p></div>",
